### Retrieve a list of Tasks [GET /tasks/?paramFilter={paramFilter}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize}&order={order}&selectfields={selectfields}]

Maximum page size is 100.

+ Parameters
    + paramFilter (optional, string) ... Must be a json encoded string.
        + taskID (string) - The task id
        + externalId (string) - External task id
        + idUserTo (number) - User id responsible for the task
        + startDate (string) - Start date filter. Format: "yyyy-MM-dd"
        + endDate (string) - End date filter. Format: "yyyy-MM-dd"
        + type (number) - Task type id
        + typeList (string) - Comma-separated list of task type ids
        + customerId (number) - Customer id
        + customerGroupId (number) - Customer group id
        + teamId (number) - Team id
        + status (number) - 0:NotFinished | 1:AutoFinished | 2:ManualFinished | 3:AutoOrManual | 4:All | 5:WithPendency | 6:StartedOrFinished | 7:InExecution
        + orientation (string) - Orientation filter
        + tags (string) - Tags filter
        + priority (number) - 1:Low | 2:Medium | 3:High
        + dateLastUpdate (string) - Filter by last update date
        + showCustomerDocument (boolean) - Include customer CPF/CNPJ
        + questionnairesId (string) - Comma-separated questionnaire ids
    + page (required, number) ... Page of the selection. Default 1.
    + pageSize (required, number) ... Amount of records. Default 10. Max 100.
    + order (required, string) ... "asc"/0 for Ascending or "desc"/1 for Descending.
    + selectfields (optional, string) ... Comma-separated field names for selective retrieval.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result": {
                "entityList": [
                    {
                        "taskID": 23,
                        "externalId": "123",
                        "idUserFrom": 123,
                        "idUserTo": 123,
                        "userToName": "Colaborador",
                        "userFromName": "Paulo",
                        "customerId": 456,
                        "taskType": 23,
                        "taskTypeDescription": "Visita Técnica",
                        "creationDate": "2016-03-23T14:10:35",
                        "taskDate": "2016-03-23T18:00:00",
                        "address": "avenue X",
                        "orientation": "Task orientation",
                        "priority": 1,
                        "finished": true,
                        "taskStatus": 5
                    }
                ],
                "pagedSearchReturnData": {
                    "order": 0,
                    "pageSize": 10,
                    "page": 1,
                    "totalItems": 50
                },
                "links": [
                    {
                        "href": "https://api.auvo.com.br/v2/Tasks?Page=1&PageSize=10&Order=Asc",
                        "rel": "self",
                        "method": "GET"
                    }
                ]
            }
        }

### Retrieve a list of Deleted Tasks [GET /tasks/GetDeletedTasks?paramFilter={paramFilter}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize}&order={order}&selectfields={selectfields}]

Returns deleted tasks. Maximum page size is 100. Same parameters and response format as the task listing endpoint above.

+ Parameters
    + paramFilter (optional, string) ... Same filter options as task listing.
    + page (required, number) ... Page of the selection. Default 1.
    + pageSize (required, number) ... Amount of records. Default 10. Max 100.
    + order (required, string) ... "asc"/0 or "desc"/1.
    + selectfields (optional, string) ... Comma-separated field names.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result": {
                "entityList": [],
                "pagedSearchReturnData": {
                    "order": 0,
                    "pageSize": 10,
                    "page": 1,
                    "totalItems": 0
                },
                "links": []
            }
        }


