    + cpfCnpj (string) - CPF or CNPJ
    + groupsId (array[number]) - List of customer group ids
    + managerTeamsId (array[number]) - List of manager team ids
    + managersId (array[number]) - List of manager user ids
    + segmentId (number) - Segment id
