### Add a new Customer - Complete [POST /customers/complete]

Register a customer with complete data including billing information, observations, and team associations by name.

+ Attributes
    + externalId (string) - External customer id. Max 255 characters
    + name (string) - Customer name. Max 500 characters
    + cpfCnpj (string) - CPF or CNPJ
    + phoneNumber (array[string]) - List of phone numbers
    + email (array[string]) - List of email addresses
    + manager (string) - Manager name. Max 500 characters
    + note (string) - Notes. Max 5000 characters
    + address (string) - Customer address
    + adressComplement (string) - Address complement. Max 1000 characters
    + latitude (number) - Address latitude
    + longitude (number) - Address longitude
    + maximumVisitTime (number) - Maximum visit time
    + unitMaximumTime (number) - Unit for maximum time
    + groups (array[string]) - List of group names
    + groupsId (array[number]) - List of group ids
    + managerTeamsId (array[number]) - Manager team ids
    + managerTeamsName (array[string]) - Manager team names
    + managersId (array[number]) - Manager user ids
    + managersName (array[string]) - Manager names
    + teamsName (array[string]) - Associated teams names
    + teamsId (array[number]) - Associated teams ids
    + segmentId (array[number]) - Segment ids
    + segmentName (string) - Segment name
    + observation (string) - Observation
    + internalObservation (string) - Internal observation
    + active (boolean) - Active status
    + talkTo (string) - Talk to
    + icmsTaxpayer (number) - ICMS taxpayer
    + stateRegistration (string) - State registration
    + municipalRegistration (string) - Municipal registration
    + billingEmail (string) - Billing email
    + billingZipCode (string) - Billing zip code
    + billingPublicArea (string) - Billing public area
    + billingAddressNumber (string) - Billing address number
    + billingAddressComplement (string) - Billing address complement
    + billingDistrict (string) - Billing district
    + billingCity (string) - Billing city
    + billingState (string) - Billing state
    + notifications (boolean) - Enable notifications
    + legalName (string) - Legal name
    + attachments (array)
        + name (string) - File name
        + file (string) - Base 64 file
    + contacts (array)
        + name (string) - Contact name
        + jobPosition (string) - Job position
        + email (string) - Contact email
        + phone (string) - Contact phone

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "externalId": "EXT-123",
                "name": "Customer Name",
                "cpfCnpj": "12345678901",
                "phoneNumber": ["11999999999"],
                "email": ["customer@email.com"],
                "address": "Rua Example, 123",
                "billingEmail": "billing@email.com",
                "billingZipCode": "74000000",
                "billingCity": "Goiânia",
                "billingState": "GO",
                "notifications": true
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    [Customer][]

### Upsert a Customer [PUT /customers/]
Update or register a new customer according to one of its identifier, `id` OR `externalId`. If `identifierBycpfCnpj` is true, also uses `cpfCnpj` as identifier.

+ Attributes
    + id (number) - Customer id
    + identifierBycpfCnpj (boolean) - Use CPF/CNPJ as identifier
    + replaceData (boolean) - Replace all data or merge. Default true
    + allowLegalNameClear (boolean) - Allow clearing legal name. Default false
    + externalId (string) - External customer id. Max 255 characters
    + name (string) - Customer name. Max 500 characters
    + phoneNumber (array[string]) - List of phone numbers
    + email (array[string]) - List of email addresses
    + manager (string) - Manager name. Max 500 characters
    + note (string) - Notes. Max 5000 characters
    + address (string) - Customer address
    + adressComplement (string) - Address complement. Max 1000 characters
    + latitude (number) - Address latitude
    + longitude (number) - Address longitude
    + cpfCnpj (string) - CPF or CNPJ
    + groupsId (array[number]) - List of customer group ids
    + managerTeamsId (array[number]) - List of manager team ids
    + managersId (array[number]) - List of manager user ids
    + segmentId (number) - Segment id
    + active (boolean) - If customer is active
    + legalName (string) - Legal name. Max 100 characters

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "externalId": "EXT-123",
                "name": "Customer Name Updated",
                "phoneNumber": ["11999999999"],
                "email": ["customer@email.com"]
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

+ Response 201 (application/json)

### Upsert a Customer - Complete [PUT /customers/complete]
Same as Upsert but with complete data including billing information.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "externalId": "EXT-123",
                "name": "Customer Name",
                "cpfCnpj": "12345678901",
                "address": "Rua Example, 123"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

+ Response 201 (application/json)

### Edit a Customer [PATCH /customers/{id}]
To update a `Customer`, send a JSONPatchDocument with updated value for one or more of the `CustomerPatch` attributes.
JsonPatch example: { "op": "replace", "path": "name", "value": "New Name" }

+ Attributes
    + name (string) - Customer name
    + externalId (string) - External customer id
    + phoneNumber (array[string]) - Phone numbers
    + email (array[string]) - Email addresses
    + manager (string) - Manager name
    + note (string) - Notes
    + address (string) - Address
    + latitude (number) - Latitude
    + longitude (number) - Longitude
    + maximumVisitTime (number) - Maximum visit time
    + unitMaximumTime (number) - Unit for maximum time
    + cpfCnpj (string) - CPF or CNPJ
    + groupsId (array[number]) - Group ids
    + managerTeamsId (array[number]) - Manager team ids
    + managersId (array[number]) - Manager ids
    + segmentId (number) - Segment id
    + active (boolean) - Active status
    + adressComplement (string) - Address complement
    + legalName (string) - Legal name

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            [
                { "op": "replace", "path": "name", "value": "New Customer Name" }
            ]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [Customer][]

### Update Customer Attachments [PUT /customers/{id}/attachments]

+ Attributes
    + removeAllAttachmentsInsertedByMe (boolean) - Remove all previous API-inserted attachments
    + attachments (array)
        + name (required, string) - File name with extension
        + file (required, string) - Base 64 file

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "removeAllAttachmentsInsertedByMe": false,
                "attachments": [
                    {
                        "name": "document.pdf",
                        "file": "base64 encoded file"
                    }
                ]
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

### Delete a Customer [DELETE /customers/{id}]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 204

### Retrieve a list of Customers [GET /customers/?paramFilter={paramFilter}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize}&order={order}&selectfields={selectfields}]

+ Parameters
    + paramFilter (optional, string) ... Must be a json encoded string.
        + id (number) - Customer id
        + description (string) - Customer name filter
        + externalId (string) - External id filter
        + segmentId (number) - Segment id filter
        + groupId (number) - Customer group id filter
        + active (boolean) - Active status filter
        + dateLastUpdate (string) - Filter by last update date
        + creationDate (string) - Filter by creation date
        + legalName (string) - Legal name filter
        + cpfCnpj (string) - CPF/CNPJ filter
    + page (required, number) ... Page. Default 1.
    + pageSize (required, number) ... Records per page. Default 10.
    + order (required, string) ... "asc"/0 or "desc"/1. Default "asc".
    + selectfields (optional, string) ... Comma-separated field names.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result": {
                "entityList": [],
                "pagedSearchReturnData": {
                    "order": 0,
                    "pageSize": 10,
                    "page": 1,
                    "totalItems": 0
                },
                "links": []
            }
        }


