# Group Task Types

## Task Type [/tasktypes/{id}]

+ Parameters

    + id (number) ... `id` of the task type.

### Retrieve a Task Type [GET /tasktypes/{id}]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            "result": {
                "id": 1,
                "description": "Task Type Name",
                "standartQuestionnaireId": null,
                "standartTime": "01:00:00",
                "sendSatisfactionSurvey": false,
                "sendDigitalOs": false,
                "active": true,
                "requirements": {
                    "fillReport": false,
                    "getSignature": false,
                    "fillRolledKilometer": false,
                    "emailTheTask": false,
                    "minimumNumberOfPhotos": 0,
                    "requiredQuestionnaires": []
                }
            }

### Add a new Task Type [POST /tasktypes/]

+ Attributes
    + description (required, string) - Task type description. Max 5000 characters
    + standartQuestionnaireId (number) - Default questionnaire id
    + standartTime (string) - Default time (processed as TimeSpan)
    + sendSatisfactionSurvey (boolean) - Send satisfaction survey. Default false
    + sendDigitalOs (boolean) - Send digital OS. Default false
    + active (boolean) - Active status. Default true
    + requirements (object) - Task type requirements
        + fillReport (boolean) - Require report fill
        + getSignature (boolean) - Require signature
        + fillRolledKilometer (boolean) - Require km input
        + emailTheTask (boolean) - Email the task
        + minimumNumberOfPhotos (number) - Minimum photos required
        + requiredQuestionnaires (array[number]) - Required questionnaire ids

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "description": "New Task Type",
                "standartTime": "01:00:00",
                "sendSatisfactionSurvey": false,
                "active": true,
                "requirements": {
                    "fillReport": true,
                    "getSignature": true,
                    "minimumNumberOfPhotos": 2
                }
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

### Edit a Task Type [PATCH /tasktypes/{id}]

+ Attributes
    + description (string) - Task type description
    + standartQuestionnaireId (number) - Default questionnaire id
    + standartTime (string) - Default time
    + sendSatisfactionSurvey (boolean)
    + sendDigitalOs (boolean)
    + active (boolean)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            [
                { "op": "replace", "path": "description", "value": "Updated Task Type" }
            ]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

### Delete a Task Type [DELETE /tasktypes/{id}]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 204

