# Group Tickets

## Ticket [/tickets/{id}]

+ Parameters

    + id (number) ... `id` of the ticket.

### Retrieve a Ticket [GET /tickets/{id}]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            "result": {
                "id": 1,
                "title": "Ticket Title",
                "description": "Ticket Description",
                "requestTypeId": 1,
                "statusId": 1,
                "requesterEmail": "requester@email.com",
                "requesterName": "Requester Name",
                "customerId": 123,
                "teamId": 1,
                "userResponsableId": 456,
                "equipmentId": 0,
                "equipmentIds": [789],
                "priority": 2,
                "externalId": "EXT-TKT-1"
            }

### Add a new Ticket [POST /tickets/]

+ Attributes
    + title (string) - Ticket title
    + description (string) - Ticket description
    + requestTypeId (number) - Request type id
    + statusId (number) - Status id
    + requesterEmail (string) - Requester email
    + requesterName (string) - Requester name
    + customerId (number) - Customer id
    + teamId (number) - Team id
    + userResponsableId (number) - Responsible user id
    + equipmentId (number) - Equipment id (single)
    + equipmentIds (array[number]) - Equipment ids (multiple)
    + priority (number) - Priority level
    + externalId (string) - External ticket id
    + customFields (array) - Custom field answers. Each item contains: customFieldTicket.id (number), value (string), valueDescription (string)
    + attachments (array)
        + name (string) - File name with extension
        + file (string) - Base 64 file

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "title": "New Ticket",
                "description": "Ticket description",
                "requestTypeId": 1,
                "statusId": 1,
                "requesterEmail": "requester@email.com",
                "requesterName": "Requester",
                "customerId": 123,
                "teamId": 1,
                "userResponsableId": 456,
                "priority": 2,
                "externalId": "EXT-TKT-1"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

### Edit a Ticket [PATCH /tickets/{id}]

+ Attributes
    + externalId (string) - External ticket id
    + statusId (number) - New status id

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            [
                { "op": "replace", "path": "statusId", "value": 2 }
            ]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

### Retrieve Ticket Request Types [GET /tickets/request-type]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result": []
        }

### Retrieve a list of Tickets [GET /tickets/?paramFilter={paramFilter}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize}&order={order}]

+ Parameters
    + paramFilter (optional, string) ... JSON encoded filter.
        + ids (string) - Comma-separated ticket ids
        + status (number) - Ticket status
        + responsableUsersIds (string) - Comma-separated responsible user ids
        + teamIds (string) - Comma-separated team ids
        + customerGroupId (number) - Customer group id
        + customerId (number) - Customer id
        + priorities (string) - Comma-separated priorities
        + openingResponsableUsersId (string) - Comma-separated opening user ids
        + externalId (string) - External ticket id
        + statusIds (string) - Comma-separated status ids
        + startDate (string) - Start date filter
        + endDate (string) - End date filter
        + startDateLastUpdate (string) - Last update start date
        + endDateLastUpdate (string) - Last update end date
        + searchTasks (boolean) - Include associated tasks
        + searchInteractions (boolean) - Include interactions
        + searchModifications (boolean) - Include modifications
        + searchCustomFields (boolean) - Include custom fields
        + searchStatusChanges (boolean) - Include status changes
    + page (required, number) ... Page. Default 1.
    + pageSize (required, number) ... Records per page. Default 10.
    + order (required, string) ... "asc"/0 or "desc"/1.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
