### Add a new Invoice [POST /invoices/]

+ Attributes
    + customerId (required, number) - Customer id
    + issueDate (required, string) - Issue date
    + responsibleUserId (number) - Responsible user id
    + subject (string) - Invoice subject
    + observations (string) - Observations
    + internalNote (string) - Internal note
    + footer (string) - Footer text
    + serviceAddress (string) - Service address
    + billingAddress (string) - Billing address
    + financialCategoryId (string) - Financial category GUID
    + discountType (string) - Discount type
    + discountValue (number) - Discount value
    + products (array) - Each item: productId (number), amount (number), unitaryValue (string)
    + services (array) - Each item: serviceId (string GUID), amount (number), unitaryValue (string)
    + additionalCosts (array) - Each item: costId (number), value (number)
    + attachments (array) - Each item: name (string), src (string)
    + payment (required, object) - Contains paymentMethods array. Each paymentMethod: paymentMethodId (string GUID), installmentsCount (number), installments array with number (number), value (number), dueDate (string), observations (string)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "customerId": 123,
                "issueDate": "2024-01-15",
                "responsibleUserId": 456,
                "subject": "New Invoice",
                "products": [
                    {
                        "productId": 1,
                        "amount": 2,
                        "unitaryValue": "10.50"
                    }
                ],
                "payment": {
                    "paymentMethods": [
                        {
                            "paymentMethodId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
                            "installmentsCount": 2,
                            "installments": [
                                {
                                    "number": 1,
                                    "value": 10.50,
                                    "dueDate": "2024-02-15",
                                    "observations": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "number": 2,
                                    "value": 10.50,
                                    "dueDate": "2024-03-15",
                                    "observations": ""
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            "result": {
                "id": 1
            }

### Update an Invoice [PUT /invoices/{id}]
Some fields are blocked after the invoice is receipted (customerId, responsibleUserId, discountType, discountValue, products, services, additionalCosts, payment).

+ Attributes
    + replaceData (boolean) - Replace all data or merge. Default true
    + customerId (number) - Customer id
    + responsibleUserId (number) - Responsible user id
    + issueDate (string) - Issue date
    + subject (string) - Invoice subject
    + observations (string) - Observations
    + internalNote (string) - Internal note
    + footer (string) - Footer text
    + serviceAddress (string) - Service address
    + billingAddress (string) - Billing address
    + financialCategoryId (string) - Financial category GUID
    + discountType (string) - Discount type
    + discountValue (number) - Discount value

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "subject": "Updated Invoice",
                "observations": "Updated notes"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            "result": {
                "publicId": 1,
                "customerId": 123,
                "customerName": "Customer Name",
