                "observations": "Updated notes",
                "privateNotes": null,
                "pageFooter": null,
                "invoiceStatus": "Open",
                "serviceAddress": "",
                "billingAddress": "",
                "financialCategory": null,
                "createdById": 456,
                "dateLastUpdate": "2024-01-20",
                "publicLink": "",
                "products": [],
                "services": [],
                "aditionalCosts": [],
                "attachment": [],
                "payment": null,
                "summary": {
                    "totalProducts": 0.00,
                    "totalServices": 0.00,
                    "totalAdditionalCosts": 0.00,
                    "grossTotalValue": 0.00,
                    "discount": {
                        "type": "Monetary",
                        "value": 0.00
                    },
                    "netTotalValue": 0.00
                },
                "invoiceChangeHistory": []
            }

### Retrieve a list of Invoices [GET /invoices/?paramFilter={paramFilter}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize}&order={order}]

Maximum page size is 100.

+ Parameters
    + paramFilter (optional, string) ... JSON encoded filter.
        + customerId (number) - Customer id filter
        + status (string) - Status filter
        + startDate (string) - Issue start date
        + endDate (string) - Issue end date
    + page (required, number) ... Page. Default 1.
    + pageSize (required, number) ... Records per page. Default 10. Max 100.
    + order (required, string) ... "asc"/0 or "desc"/1.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result": {
                "entityList": [],
                "pagedSearchReturnData": {
                    "order": 0,
                    "pageSize": 10,
                    "page": 1,
                    "totalItems": 0
                },
                "links": []
            }
        }


# Group Quotations

## Quotation [/quotations/{id}]

+ Parameters

    + id (number) ... `id` of the quotation.

### Retrieve a Quotation [GET /quotations/{id}]

**Notes:**
- `taskIds`: returns an empty array `[]` when the quotation has no associated tasks.
- `payment`: returns `null` when the quotation has no installments.
- `leadName`: returns `null` when a customer is associated (customerId > 0).
- `internalNote`: returns `null` when empty.

