### Add a new Quotation [POST /quotations/]

+ Attributes
    + statusId (number) - Status id
    + customerId (number) - Customer id
    + leadName (string) - Lead name (if no customer)
    + responsibleUserId (number) - Responsible user id
    + requestDate (string) - Request date
    + expireDate (string) - Expiration date
    + externalCode (string) - External code
    + observations (string) - Observations
    + internalNote (string) - Internal note
    + discountType (string) - Discount type
    + discountValue (number) - Discount value
    + taskId (number) - Associated task id
    + taskIds (array[number]) - Associated task ids
    + products (array) - Each item: productId (number), amount (number), unitaryValue (string), unitaryDiscount with type (string) and value (number)
    + services (array) - Each item: serviceId (string GUID), amount (number), unitaryValue (string), unitaryDiscount with type (string) and value (number)
    + additionalCosts (array) - Each item: costId (number), value (number)
    + attachments (array) - Each item: name (string), src (string), visibleToClient (boolean)
    + payment (object) - Contains installments array. Each installment: number (number), value (number), dueDate (string), paymentMethod.id (string GUID)

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "statusId": 1,
                "customerId": 123,
                "responsibleUserId": 456,
                "requestDate": "2024-01-15",
                "expireDate": "2024-02-15",
                "observations": "New quotation"
