### Add Service to Quotation [POST /quotations/{id}/services/{idService}]

+ Parameters
    + id (number) ... Quotation id.
    + idService (string) ... Service GUID.

+ Attributes
    + serviceId (string) - Service GUID
    + externalCode (string) - External code
    + name (string) - Service name
    + description (string) - Description
    + amount (number) - Quantity
    + unitaryValue (string) - Unit value
    + unitaryDiscount (object)
        + type (string) - Discount type
        + value (number) - Discount value

