        + customersId (array[number]) - Customer ids
        + productsId (array[number]) - Product ids
        + requestStartDate (string) - Request start date
        + requestEndDate (string) - Request end date
        + lastUpdateStartDate (string) - Last update start date
        + lastUpdateEndDate (string) - Last update end date
        + currentStage (string) - Current stage filter (comma-separated)
