# Group Receivables

## Receivable [/receivables/{id}]

+ Parameters

    + id (number) ... `id` of the receivable.

### Retrieve a Receivable [GET /receivables/{id}]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            "result": {
                "id": 1,
                "customerId": 123,
                "bankAccountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
                "value": 100.00,
                "dueDate": "2024-02-15",
                "competencyDate": "2024-01-15",
                "description": "Service payment",
                "observations": "Notes",
                "discount": 0,
                "surcharge": 0,
                "financialCategoryId": null,
                "paymentMethodId": null,
                "paid": false,
                "paidDate": null,
                "paidValue": null
            }

### Add a new Receivable [POST /receivables/]

+ Attributes
    + customerId (required, number) - Customer id
    + bankAccountId (required, string) - Bank account GUID
    + value (required, number) - Receivable value
    + dueDate (required, string) - Due date
    + competencyDate (string) - Competency date
    + description (string) - Description. Max 500 characters
    + observations (string) - Observations. Max 1000 characters
    + discount (number) - Discount value
    + surcharge (number) - Surcharge value
    + financialCategoryId (string) - Financial category GUID
    + paymentMethodId (string) - Payment method GUID
    + paid (boolean) - Payment status
    + paidDate (string) - Payment date
    + paidValue (number) - Payment value
    + isRecurrent (boolean) - Is recurrent
    + recurrenceType (string) - "daily" | "weekly" | "biweekly" | "monthly" | "bimonthly" | "quarterly" | "yearly"
    + recurrenceDueDate (string) - Recurrence due date
    + recurrenceLimitDate (string) - Recurrence limit date
    + considerWeekends (boolean) - Consider weekends

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "customerId": 123,
                "bankAccountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
                "value": 100.00,
                "dueDate": "2024-02-15",
                "description": "Service payment",
                "paid": false
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

### Update a Receivable [PUT /receivables/{id}]

+ Attributes
    + bankAccountId (string) - Bank account GUID
    + value (number) - Value
    + dueDate (string) - Due date
    + competencyDate (string) - Competency date
    + description (string) - Description. Max 500 characters
    + observations (string) - Observations. Max 1000 characters
    + discount (number) - Discount
    + surcharge (number) - Surcharge
    + financialCategoryId (string) - Financial category GUID
    + paymentMethodId (string) - Payment method GUID
    + paid (boolean) - Payment status
    + paidDate (string) - Payment date
    + paidValue (number) - Payment value

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "bankAccountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
                "value": 150.00,
                "dueDate": "2024-03-15",
                "paid": true,
                "paidDate": "2024-03-10",
                "paidValue": 150.00
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

### Retrieve a list of Receivables [GET /receivables/?paramFilter={paramFilter}&page={page}&pageSize={pageSize}&order={order}]

Maximum page size is 100.

+ Parameters
    + paramFilter (optional, string) ... JSON encoded filter.
        + customerId (number) - Customer id
        + bankAccountId (string) - Bank account GUID
        + status (number) - Status (0, 1, 2, or 4)
        + isRecurrent (boolean) - Is recurrent filter
        + dueDateFrom (string) - Due date from
        + dueDateTo (string) - Due date to
    + page (required, number) ... Page. Default 1.
    + pageSize (required, number) ... Records per page. Default 100. Max 100.
    + order (required, string) ... "asc"/0 or "desc"/1.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "result": {
                "entityList": [],
                "pagedSearchReturnData": {
                    "order": 0,
                    "pageSize": 100,
                    "page": 1,
                    "totalItems": 0
                },
                "links": []
            }
        }


