### Add a new Service Order [POST /serviceorders/]

+ Attributes
    + customerId (required, number) - Customer id
    + statusId (required, string) - Status GUID
    + description (required, string) - Order description
    + externalCode (string) - External code
    + dateFirstVisit (string) - First visit date
    + dateLastVisit (string) - Last visit date
    + startTime (string) - Start time "HH:mm"
    + duration (number) - Duration in minutes
    + taskTypeId (number) - Task type id
    + defaultQuestionnaireId (number) - Default questionnaire id
    + defaultResponsibleId (number) - Default responsible user id
    + priority (number) - Priority (default 2)
    + financialCategoryId (string) - Financial category GUID
    + keywordsIds (array[number]) - Keyword ids
    + attachments (array)
        + name (string) - File name
        + file (string) - Base 64 file
    + recurrenceType (string) - "daily" | "weekly" | "monthly" | "yearly"
    + recurrenceInterval (number) - Recurrence interval
    + recurrenceDays (array[number]) - Days of week (1-7: 1=Sun...7=Sat)
    + monthlyMode (string) - "dayOfMonth" | "dayOfWeek"

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer token

    + Body

            {
                "customerId": 123,
                "statusId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
                "description": "New Service Order",
                "priority": 2,
                "taskTypeId": 1,
                "keywordsIds": [1, 2]
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

### Edit a Service Order [PATCH /serviceorders/{code}]

+ Parameters
    + code (number) ... Project code.

+ Attributes
    + externalId (string) - External id (query parameter)
    + descricao (string) - Description (query parameter)
